pan></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nlAuxnL.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/daby3TA.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gHwjWGV.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QqquBKr.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Going to add my own story to this.

Me: Son, I'm trans.
Him (8 at the time): Really?

Me: Really.

Him: Really Really??

Me (on the edge of tears, barely holding it together, fearful of what his reaction might be): Yes, I'm a woman.

Him: ...

Me: I want you to know I'll always love you.

Him (deep in thought): ...

Me (tears rolling now): Do... do you have any questions?

Him: ... will I be let off my chores?
Me: No, you still need to empty the dishwasher.

Him: ... will I get extra candy?
Me: No, you having two mommies doesn't get you more candy.

Wife (nods firmly at the no-extra-candy rule)
Me: Do you have any more questions?
Him: ...can I tell you about the movie I just saw with grandma?

Me: Any questions about me being trans.
Him: So I use she and her for you now like for other girls?

Me: Yes.
Him: OK... I love you mommy. Anyway... grandmapickedmeupfromschool. WewenttothemoviesandgotpopcornandIhadawholethingofitand (pause for breath) thereisthiskidcalledBillyBatsonbuthebecomesSHAZAM! (pause for breath) andhefightsdemonsandtherewasawizardheisplayedbythe (pause for breath) guyfromchuckwhoplayschuckyouknowthespyand (pause for breath) hischestlightsupandhehaslightningandissuperstrongbutnotascoolatheFlash...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tuaAIzM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThatOtherGirlYouKnow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Here’s a small dog dump to brighten your day!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9wvPCJD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a0UauIL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4TkYDJE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BfiBa5y.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/o1XHyCm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5s0UrPR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tlNQuP4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fYHplGv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gcH5TA7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Fuf52Ky.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mtf15sH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GyyUh2W.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: 